_sText:
This is the final version to my gg_deagle5_cube series. I wanted to get an initial version out before I left for my trip so I didnt get to do any optimizing which wasnt one of my better decisions. I have optimized this map to the best of my ability (thank you lost and crazypip for guidance) I hope that you enjoy this new version of my map.
Special Thanks Here are some people that I want to thank for helping me make my map the best it can be.
  • Greyfrog - Thank you for helping me optimize and make the map look a lot cooler.
  • Crazypip666 - Thank you for instructing me where to place my func_details
  • Ownt -Thank you for giving me feedback on my map
  • HacksawJack - Thank you for making the custom logo for my map
  • My Studio - Thank you also for helping me and giving me feedback
Edit 8/6/08: I updated the .bsp with minor bug fixes.
  • Fixed catwalk ramps not touching the floor
  • Removed bumps in floor due to disorientation
Thanks!
